deck: Featuring the cast from "Love Live! Sunshine", Yohane the Parhelion: BLAZE in the DEEPBLUE is a 2D metroidvania game set in an underwater labyrinth. Players explore dungeons, craft equipment from collected materials, and seek to rescue Yohane's missing friends amidst a backdrop of changing layouts and hidden areas within the dungeon.
name: Yohane the Parhelion: BLAZE in the DEEPBLUE

deck: On Xbox Series X, Steam and PS5
name: Disorder

deck: The Lonesome Guild is an action RPG from Tiny Bull Studios and Don't Nod. As an amnesiac ghost, players gather together a team to combat a loneliness epidemic sweeping across the globe.
name: The Lonesome Guild

deck: Monster Train 2 is the sequel to the hit rogue-like deck-builder from Shiny Shoe.
name: Monster Train 2

deck: Styx: Blades of Greed is the third entry in a series of stealth action games from Cyanide Studio, which began as an offshoot from Of Orcs and Men.
name: Styx: Blades of Greed

deck: Search Action with emphasis on combat, using 3D models
name: The Devil Within: Satgat

deck: Light zombie survival game with base building and zombie companions.
name: Welcome to ParadiZe

deck: A VR puzzle-adventure game from Fireproof Games.
name: Ghost Town

deck: Starseeker is a multiplayer exploration game set in the same universe as Astroneer.
name: Starseeker: Astroneer Expeditions

deck: The second game in the Dollhouse series. The main character Eliza de Moor tries to recover her memories by using a experimental drug that turns reality into a labyrinth of her own forgotten memories.
name: Dollhouse: Behind the Broken Mirror

deck: A roguelite shooter similar in style to Starfox.
name: Whisker Squadron

deck: Nineteen years after it was originally released, Bethesda Game Studios' epic, open-world, role-playing game receives a full graphical overhaul with numerous quality of life upgrades.
name: The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion Remastered

deck: A fantasy life sim game set in the seaside town of Mossport where you play a witch-in-training enrolled at Witchbrook College.
name: Witchbrook

deck: From the studio behind the Hitman series comes a new origin story for Britain's famous secret agent James Bond.
name: 007 First Light

deck: During an event celebrating the second anniversary of the original game, it was revealed that the team is working on a sequel.
name: Daemon X Machina: Titanic Scion

deck: A 3D Kirby adventure on Nintendo Switch.
name: Kirby and the Forgotten Land
